To send code to github
git add --all
git commit -m "My comment"
git push

To download code
git pull

Helpful shortcut commands -- feel free to correct any of these
ctrl alt l --> cleans all line of code
ctrl d --> duplicates current line of code
shift f10 --> play specified page of code
ctrl shift f10 --> play page of code currently looked at
shift enter --> open a blank line even if you were in the middle of another line
ctrl / --> comment a line of code, can be used after highlighting multiple lines